text: My step father was abusive most of my childhood so when I watched this movie I could really relate to it. I watched my step father go from being a monster into a loving grandfather to my children. Broke my heart when I heard he was suffering from cancer because all those times he beat me I wished he die or feel the pain he inflected on me. I went to a Christian therapist who told me to write down all the bad things people have done to me in my life and rip it up and pray a s I prayed I told God I forgave each person who harmed me in anyway. You have to forgive those who harmed you in order for God to forgive you. The first time I heard this song I was at a Christian youth group retreat. It has always been one of my favorites but now that I know the story behind it I'm forever grateful someone like Bart told jus story and turned it into something beautiful
